# Polygon Amoy Testnet Configuration
PRIVATE_KEY=your_private_key_here
POLYGONSCAN_API_KEY=your_polygonscan_api_key_here

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env
# 2. Add your wallet private key (the one with MATIC for gas fees)
# 3. Get a free API key from https://polygonscan.com/apis
# 4. Run: npm run deploy:amoy
# 5. Copy the deployed contract address to your main .env file

# How to get your private key:
# 1. Open MetaMask
